{"tid":1631412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊擊戰，免gear，著多件T-shirt 係身，裝修工具放係草叢","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:41.000Z","uid":771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6127bfe8e2f421d7d08aa5e02958d5d11a953a5c","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"裝修完化身路人，真正既be water <br />\n<br />\n背狼都唔洗拎，跑都跑得快d <br />\n<br />\n黑衫黑褲<br />\n<br />\n著多件其他色t-shirt 係入面，隨時變身"},{"pid":"89b5839073483a6ac1a1afa419f9d756030863eb","tid":1631412,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e18bbc7e9d3cb2f4647d21bcb861e6a36c4d5aa","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"裝修工具現場拎<br />\n<br />\n自備工具放草叢"},{"pid":"a88f33f81b1fcb50a054fe717dd1e736969471a8","tid":1631412,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95fcd96d2e49572cd0bd90c8990c3ba301315ae2","tid":1631412,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66d425cadaf31e61bd09058c05600414035de7ce","tid":1631412,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e18bbc7e9d3cb2f4647d21bcb861e6a36c4d5aa","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"裝修工具現場拎<br />\n<br />\n自備工具放草叢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"就地取材"},{"pid":"01b8595609c545e7971a3c81101465022e8b8ba8","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8a1efa19d380db75f4b634e2f612605ed3e8c1a","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30dddd50c3900b75d9aebb060b78a8dbf7879859","tid":1631412,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d425cadaf31e61bd09058c05600414035de7ce","tid":1631412,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e18bbc7e9d3cb2f4647d21bcb861e6a36c4d5aa","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"裝修工具現場拎<br />\n<br />\n自備工具放草叢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"就地取材"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"就地野未必啱洗"},{"pid":"11a5d14891af97b3866831abe7b6e542c0d43523","tid":1631412,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcc9b6d0d96da68070265465fa034a55180bd650","tid":1631412,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"84f81af500c2d56c722e7ace4304070e02773893","tid":1631412,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}